---
// Componente CTA (Call To Action) - Sección final de conversión
---

<section class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-turismo-secondary to-turismo-primary py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-turismo-highlight/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-48 -mt-48"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-turismo-highlight/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-48 -mb-48"></div>

  <!-- Contenido -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    
    <!-- Título principal -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 animate-fade-in">
      Comenzá a Planear Tu Viaje Hoy
    </h2>

    <!-- Subtítulo -->
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-turismo-highlight mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      No esperes más. Descubre los destinos que siempre soñaste visitar. Nuestro equipo está listo para ayudarte a crear la experiencia de viaje perfecta.
    </p>

    <!-- Botones de acción -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      
      <!-- Botón principal -->
      <button 
        class="px-10 md:px-14 py-4 md:py-5 bg-turismo-highlight text-turismo-secondary font-bold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-white transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl cursor-pointer"
      >
        Reservar Ahora
      </button>

      <!-- Botón secundario -->
      <button 
        class="px-10 md:px-14 py-4 md:py-5 border-2 border-white text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-turismo-secondary transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer"
      >
        Contactar Asesor
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Información adicional -->
    <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-white">
      
      <div class="animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-turismo-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="font-bold mb-1">Respuesta Rápida</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-turismo-highlight">En menos de 24 horas</p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-turismo-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m7 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="font-bold mb-1">100% Seguro</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-turismo-highlight">Garantía de satisfacción</p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-turismo-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5-4a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="font-bold mb-1">Soporte 24/7</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-turismo-highlight">Siempre disponibles</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.7s ease-in-out forwards;
  }

  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slideUp 0.7s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>
